
Dominos
Rob Shaw rob@protolife.com
Norman Packard n@protolife.com
circa 2008-2016

Montecarlo random walk of dominos on a lattice, with hard core exclusion.
Constraints on rotation are variable (see keys 5,6,7 in the interactive simulation).

"Leaky Membrane Dynamics" Robert S. Shaw and Norman H. Packard, Phys. Rev. Lett. 105, 098102 â€“ Published 26 August 2010

tested on Mac OS X 10.8-10.11

Set resolution in domgrav.h to vary size of dominos on the screen.

With focus in graphics window, "h" will print interactive keys in launch window.

Please reference and inform authors if used in research.


